    <h6><em>Limitations</em></h6>

    <p>It is important to note that these data only consist of arrests and should not be taken as an indicator of actual guilt.  Additionally, many crimes may go undetected for which no arrests can occur.</p>

    <p>Lastly, the arrest data for 2016 is incomplete and only current up to and including November.  Any interpretations that include the year 2016 should be approached with caution.</p>



